    "In this book he thoroughly studied multiple aspects of Rembrandt\u2019s studio practice, his method of working, and his painting technique, taking into account contemporary art-theoretical literature.": [],
    "In addition to his teaching and professional work, Van de Wetering was eager to communicate his insights to a larger audience, with an active program of lectures and public appearances.": [],
